              )
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \sigma _{xy}={\frac {d\ln(y/x)}{d\ln(MRT_{12})}}={\frac {d\ln(y/x)}{d\ln(F_{x}/F_{y})}}}
  
If 
  
    
      
        
